TY  - JOUR
TI  - Kernels of Preference Structures
AU  - White, D. J.
AB  - [A kernel of a set of alternative actions over which there is a partial order is defined in terms of optimality properties. It is shown to be the same as the generalized efficient set. A variety of theorems such as uniqueness, existence, and composition in terms of other sets are established. Related sets, such as quasi kernels and weak kernels, are also considered.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jan., 1977
