TY  - JOUR
TI  - Non-Price Rationing of Intermediate Goods in Centrally Planned Economies: A Comment
AU  - Murrell, Peter
AU  - Green, Donald W.
AB  - [This paper investigates an operational inconsistency between the constrained priority rationing scheme introduced by Manove in 1973 and the criterion used to determine an "optimal" priority matrix. A truncation of the optimality criterion is suggested in order to resolve this inconsistency and also reduce a potential source of bias against final demand.]
